"```sql\nSELECT schools.School\nFROM satscores\nJOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode\nWHERE satscores.NumTstTakr > 500 AND schools.Magnet = 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the names of schools from the `schools` table that have more than 500 SAT test takers and are identified as magnet schools or offer a magnet program. The query joins the `satscores` and `schools` tables using the foreign key relationship between `satscores.cds` and `schools.CDSCode`."